    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at the required Gradation 1 level. Validation results demonstrate RH MAPE of 6.2% and pressure-head MAPE of 4.1%, both within pre-specified acceptance criteria. The assessment team determined that the validation evidence generated under solver build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2 is applicable to the released production build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7 on the basis that the rc2-to-release transition involved only a version-tag change with no functional code modifications, and therefore re-execution of the validation campaign was not warranted. The COU1 credibility assessment is accepted at Medium assurance level for the Class II CPB device hemolysis prediction application.",
